2025-06-26FIN, GACCustoms TariffOrder Imposing a Surtax on the Importation of Certain Steel GoodsOrder Imposing a Surtax on the Importation of Certain Steel Goods in order to (1) impose temporary trade measures in the form of a tariff rate quota for one year on imports of flat, long, pipe and tube, semi-finished, stainless steel products; and (2) permit a volume of imports of specified steel goods corresponding to 2024 import volumes.Registration: SOR/2025-0148 Publication Date: 2025-07-16
subject: Order Imposing a Surtax on the Importation of Certain Steel Goods
precis: Order Imposing a Surtax on the Importation of Certain Steel Goods in order to (1) impose temporary trade measures in the form of a tariff rate quota for one year on imports of flat, long, pipe and tube, semi-finished, stainless steel products; and (2) permit a volume of imports of specified steel goods corresponding to 2024 import volumes.
